            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Personalised subject lines lift open rates by roughly 26% (Campaign Monitor). McKinsey reports full personalization can reduce acquisition costs by 50% and boost revenue 5-15% for consumer brands.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
