              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Segmentation groups subscribers so different groups receive different emails. Personalization customises content for individuals within a group — using merge tags, dynamic blocks, or send-time optimisation. Segmentation usually comes first.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

